nodes.text: Animal Instincts was the name given to the younglings who joined Preigo's circus to infiltrate the Ohnaka Gang and rescue Ahsoka Tano on Florrum.

The younglings claimed to be acrobats and were presented to Hondo Ohnaka. Petro was dressed as a gundark, Zatt was a rancor, and Gungi was a narglatch. Despite their group name, Katooni and Byph were not dressed as animals, although the latter was adorned with tree blossoms from Carlac.
